This file documents Release 2.1 (beta) of IRC


The release consists of the source code in the top level directory.
Other directories are:


doc        documentation and installation guide
contrib    various contributed programs
services   various IRC services (currently wumpus and diplomacy)



Installation Note:

     Change the SYS variable in the Makefile as appropriate and
     do 'make config'.  The default setup is for bsd, which is
     correct for most machines.
 
Note:  This release does not support simple VMS configuration.

Note:  The conf.setup script in contrib is an alternative method
       of setting up the configuration file.
 
